{
  "id": "plugin-command",
  "title": "/plugin — Extend Claude Code",
  "description": "Tutorial sobre el comando /plugin: descubrir, instalar y crear plugins para Claude Code",
  "fps": 30,
  "width": 1280,
  "height": 720,
  "theme": "linea-directa",
  "scenes": [
    {
      "type": "intro",
      "title": "/plugin",
      "subtitle": "Extiende Claude Code con plugins compartibles",
      "durationInSeconds": 4
    },
    {
      "type": "terminal",
      "title": "Explorar plugins disponibles",
      "lines": [
        { "kind": "command", "text": "/plugin" },
        { "kind": "blank", "text": "", "delayAfterMs": 600 },
        { "kind": "output", "text": "┌─ Discover ─┬─ Installed ─┬─ Marketplaces ─┬─ Errors ─┐" },
        { "kind": "output", "text": "│                                                       │" },
        { "kind": "output", "text": "│  Official Marketplace:                                │" },
        { "kind": "output", "text": "│   Code Intelligence                                  │" },
        { "kind": "output", "text": "│   ├── pyright-lsp         Python type checking        │" },
        { "kind": "output", "text": "│   ├── typescript-lsp      TypeScript/JavaScript       │" },
        { "kind": "output", "text": "│   └── rust-analyzer-lsp   Rust                        │" },
        { "kind": "output", "text": "│                                                       │" },
        { "kind": "output", "text": "│   External Integrations                               │" },
        { "kind": "output", "text": "│   ├── github              Source control              │" },
        { "kind": "output", "text": "│   ├── slack               Communication              │" },
        { "kind": "output", "text": "│   └── sentry              Monitoring                 │" },
        { "kind": "output", "text": "│                                                       │" },
        { "kind": "output", "text": "│  Type to filter...             (45 plugins available)  │" },
        { "kind": "output", "text": "└───────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘" }
      ],
      "durationInSeconds": 10
    },
    {
      "type": "callout",
      "text": "Un plugin empaqueta skills, agents, hooks, MCP servers y LSP servers en un solo paquete compartible — con namespace automático para evitar conflictos.",
      "position": "bottom",
      "background": "overlay",
      "durationInSeconds": 5
    },
    {
      "type": "terminal",
      "title": "Instalar un plugin",
      "lines": [
        { "kind": "command", "text": "/plugin install github@claude-plugins-official" },
        { "kind": "blank", "text": "", "delayAfterMs": 800 },
        { "kind": "output", "text": "✓ Plugin installed: github@claude-plugins-official" },
        { "kind": "output", "text": "  Scope: user  |  Version: 1.2.3" },
        { "kind": "blank", "text": "" },
        { "kind": "command", "text": "/reload-plugins", "delayAfterMs": 600 },
        { "kind": "blank", "text": "", "delayAfterMs": 400 },
        { "kind": "output", "text": "Reloaded plugins:" },
        { "kind": "output", "text": "  Skills: 5 new  |  Agents: 2  |  Hooks: 3  |  MCP: 1" }
      ],
      "durationInSeconds": 10
    },
    {
      "type": "terminal",
      "title": "Crear tu propio plugin",
      "lines": [
        { "kind": "command", "text": "mkdir -p my-plugin/.claude-plugin" },
        { "kind": "blank", "text": "", "delayAfterMs": 300 },
        { "kind": "claude", "text": "Creo plugin.json con nombre, descripción y versión..." },
        { "kind": "output", "text": "  ✓ Created .claude-plugin/plugin.json", "delayAfterMs": 400 },
        { "kind": "blank", "text": "" },
        { "kind": "claude", "text": "Añado un skill en skills/hello/SKILL.md..." },
        { "kind": "output", "text": "  ✓ Created skills/hello/SKILL.md", "delayAfterMs": 400 },
        { "kind": "blank", "text": "" },
        { "kind": "command", "text": "claude --plugin-dir ./my-plugin", "delayAfterMs": 600 },
        { "kind": "blank", "text": "", "delayAfterMs": 400 },
        { "kind": "command", "text": "/my-plugin:hello Alex" },
        {
          "kind": "claude",
          "text": "¡Hola Alex! Soy tu plugin personalizado. ¿En qué puedo ayudarte?",
          "delayAfterMs": 500
        }
      ],
      "durationInSeconds": 14
    },
    {
      "type": "callout",
      "text": "¿Cuándo usar plugins vs .claude/skills/? Empieza con standalone para iterar rápido. Convierte a plugin cuando quieras compartir con tu equipo o distribuir en un marketplace.",
      "position": "top",
      "background": "solid",
      "durationInSeconds": 5
    },
    {
      "type": "outro",
      "title": "Plugins en Claude Code",
      "bullets": [
        "/plugin — gestor interactivo con 4 pestañas",
        "Instala desde marketplace: /plugin install nombre@marketplace",
        "Crea el tuyo: .claude-plugin/plugin.json + skills/",
        "Prueba en local: claude --plugin-dir ./mi-plugin",
        "Siempre ejecuta /reload-plugins tras cambios"
      ],
      "durationInSeconds": 6
    }
  ]
}
